label: A8 Access Impacted
definition: Where the right of access of personal data is impacted
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Denied
definition: Where the protection of personal data is denied to be applicable or required
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Eroded
definition: Where the protection of personal data is affected negatively systematically and over time
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 ExercisePrevented
definition: Where the protection of personal data is prevented from being carried out
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Limited
definition: Where not all personal data has been protected or adequately protected
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Obstructed
definition: Where barriers are created or are present to protect personal data
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Processing with Nonspecific Purposes
definition: Where there is processing of personal data for or with non-specific purposes i.e. processing is not limited to specific purposes
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Processing without Valid Consent
definition: Where there is processing of personal data without valid consent where consent is the valid legal basis as established in law
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Processing without Valid Legal Basis
definition: Where there is processing of personal data without a valid legal basis established in law
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

definition: A8 Protection Of Personal Data

definition: Something that acts as or is considered as an impact on A8 Protection Of Personal Data

label: A8 Rectificiation Impacted
definition: Where the right of rectification of personal data is impacted
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Unfair Processing
definition: Where there is unfair processing of personal data
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Unfulfilled
definition: Where the protection of personal data is not carried out
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions

label: A8 Violated
definition: Where the right to protection of personal data is violated
scopenote: This concept is experimental and may change in future versions
